### AidFlow API — Reports endpoints
# REST Client extension: click 'Send Request' above each block

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_TOKEN

### Program summary report (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/programs/PROGRAM_ID/summary
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Distribution report (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/distribution?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-04-30
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Beneficiary reach report (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/beneficiaries?programId=PROGRAM_ID
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Audit log (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/audit?entity=batch&entityId=BATCH_ID
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
